data.Name: Los Toms
data.Bio: Los Toms are an American psychedelic rock band formed in Fort Collins, Colorado. The band consists of Jerel Teichroew (guitar, vocals), Casey Garrow (guitar, vocals), Nately Dorlac (bass, synthesizer, vocals) and Giovanni Manwaring (drums). They were originated through late-night heavy jam sessions in a poorly-wired, abandoned airplane hangar on 2017. They started off into their psychedelic journey with The Sticker EP (2019), consisting of tracks such as Surf Roach and Ziggurat. Read more on Last.fm
